# Backend API Configuration
# The API path to use when communicating with the NeMo Agent toolkit backend.
# Supported values:
#   /chat           - Non-streaming chat endpoint (NAT default)
#   /chat/stream    - Streaming chat endpoint (NAT default, recommended)
#   /generate       - Non-streaming generate endpoint
#   /generate/stream - Streaming generate endpoint
#   /v1/chat/completions - OpenAI-compatible endpoint (single endpoint, uses stream param)
BACKEND_API_PATH=/chat/stream
